verbose_text: In our previous study, we have reported that treatment with a mixture of FA-chitosan with mouse IP-10 plasmid (FA-chitosan / mIP-10) inhibited tumor growth and angiogenesis, and promoted apoptosis of tumor cells in mice XREF_BIBR.
